Wednesday, January 28, 1998

MERIT DOCKET

97-779. Cincinnati Bell Tel. Co. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 95-845-TP-COI. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss’ sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, F.E. Sweeney, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur. Pfeifer, dissents. Resnick, J., not participating.
